{"id":720,"date":"2024-02-10T09:59:37","date_gmt":"2024-02-10T09:59:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/araha.org\/?p=720"},"modified":"2024-02-10T09:59:37","modified_gmt":"2024-02-10T09:59:37","slug":"partner-with-araha-to-send-6-million-meals-overseas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/araha.org\/partner-with-araha-to-send-6-million-meals-overseas\/","title":{"rendered":"Partner with WorldKind Relief  to Send 6-Million Meals Overseas!"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>As part of our drought relief effort, WorldKind Relief  is shipping 6,804,000 meals to vulnerable people in the Horn of Africa, but we need your help to get this done!<\/p><p>Global supply chain issues have caused a significant increase in transportation costs and we need additional funding to ship 25 cargo containers of fortified rice packs to families who are on the brink of starvation. Our field team has identified a long wait list of beneficiaries who are in desperate need of food assistance but we need to get these shipments out by the end of the year.&nbsp;<\/p><p>Not only is this an important cause that will provide life sustaining nutrition to thousands of families, especially children, but this is an excellent opportunity for your business to be recognized internationally as a philanthropic partner. The value of this kind of social currency can be extremely beneficial in gaining support from your consumer base. WorldKind Relief  has over 250,000 followers across several social media platforms. We can provide your business with positive media exposure that will sharpen your competitive edge. Our organization employs a photojournalist to capture every aspect of the project and we will feature your logo or chosen dedication on our banner. We will work with you to create a marketing strategy that will benefit your company.&nbsp;<\/p><p>Each container costs $15,000, which includes shipment from the United State to the Horn of Africa, customs fees, in-land transportation, and distribution. WorldKind Relief  is a registered 501c3 and your donation is tax deductible.&nbsp;<\/p><p>Please email Hope at&nbsp; developmentdirector@araha.org if you\u2019d like to discuss a partnership or if you need any additional information about this project. Please don\u2019t hesitate to reach out, we are always looking to strengthen our partnerships and are open to tailoring a project to fit your philanthropic needs.&nbsp;<\/p><figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"994\" data-id=\"722\" src=\"https:\/\/araha.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/shippingcontainers-768x994-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-722\" srcset=\"https:\/\/araha.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/shippingcontainers-768x994-1.png 768w, https:\/\/araha.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/shippingcontainers-768x994-1-600x777.png 600w, https:\/\/araha.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/shippingcontainers-768x994-1-232x300.png 232w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"994\" data-id=\"723\" src=\"https:\/\/araha.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/shipping3-768x994-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-723\" srcset=\"https:\/\/araha.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/shipping3-768x994-1.png 768w, https:\/\/araha.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/shipping3-768x994-1-600x777.png 600w, https:\/\/araha.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/shipping3-768x994-1-232x300.png 232w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" \/><\/figure><\/figure>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>As part of our drought relief effort, WorldKind Relief  is shipping 6,804,000 meals to vulnerable people in the Horn of Africa, [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":